In [5]:
# Calculating number of unique x_data along the streamwise direction(x_direction)

row_num = data.shape[0]   # Returns the number of rows
print(row_num)

x_dataset = pd.DataFrame(columns=['unique_x_coordinate'])
i=0

for n in range(row_num):
    if n < (row_num-1):
         if data['x_coordinate'].values[n] != data['x_coordinate'].values[n+1]:
                x_dataset.loc[i,"unique_x_coordinate"] = data['x_coordinate'].values[n]
                i=i+1
    elif n==(row_num-1):
        x_dataset.loc[i,"unique_x_coordinate"] = data['x_coordinate'].values[row_num-1]
        
        
print(x_dataset)

In [6]:
# Calculating mixing efficiency corresponding to each unique_x_coordinate using a for loop

row_unique = x_dataset.shape[0]
print(row_unique)

Result_dataset = pd.DataFrame(columns=['x_coordinate','Total Pressure Recovery'])

for ii in range(row_unique):
    cal_dataset = data[x_dataset.loc[ii,"unique_x_coordinate"]==data.loc[:,"x_coordinate"]]
    cal_dataset = cal_dataset.reset_index(drop=True)
    cal_dataset_row = cal_dataset.shape[0]
    
    #Finding Area
    for kk in range(cal_dataset_row):
        if kk>0 :
            cal_dataset.loc[kk,'y_difference'] = cal_dataset.loc[kk,'y_coordinate']-cal_dataset.loc[kk-1,'y_coordinate']
        elif kk==0:
            cal_dataset.loc[kk,'y_difference'] = cal_dataset.loc[kk,'y_coordinate']
            
    for m in range(cal_dataset_row):
        if m==0 :
            cal_dataset.loc[m,'dA'] = cal_dataset.loc[m,'y_difference']/2
        elif m < (cal_dataset_row - 1):
            cal_dataset.loc[m,"dA"] = (cal_dataset.loc[m,'y_difference']+cal_dataset.loc[m+1,'y_difference'])/2
        elif m == (cal_dataset_row-1) :
            cal_dataset.loc[m,'dA'] = cal_dataset.loc[m,'y_difference']/2
            
    # Integral Individual Result Data
    for p in range(cal_dataset_row):
        cal_dataset.loc[p,'total_pressure_recovery_numerator'] = cal_dataset.loc[p,'density']*cal_dataset.loc[p,'x_velocity']*cal_dataset.loc[p,'Total_Pressure']*cal_dataset.loc[p,'dA']
        cal_dataset.loc[p,'total_pressure_recovery_denominator'] = cal_dataset.loc[p,'density']*cal_dataset.loc[p,'x_velocity']*cal_dataset.loc[p,'dA']
    
    total_numerator = sum(cal_dataset.loc[:,'total_pressure_recovery_numerator'])
    total_denominator = sum(cal_dataset.loc[:,'total_pressure_recovery_denominator'])
    total_result = total_numerator/total_denominator
    
    
    
    Result_dataset.loc[ii,'x_coordinate'] = x_dataset.loc[ii,'unique_x_coordinate']
    Result_dataset.loc[ii,'Avg_total_pressure'] = total_result
    print(cal_dataset)

    
# Finding maximum pressure to calculate total pressure recovery
max_pressure = Result_dataset['Avg_total_pressure'].max()

Result_dataset.loc[:,'Total Pressure Recovery'] = Result_dataset.loc[:,'Avg_total_pressure']/max_pressure

print(Result_dataset)

# Plotting the final graph
#plt.rcParams["font.family"] = "Times New Roman"

x_data = Result_dataset.loc[:,'x_coordinate']
y_data = Result_dataset.loc[:,"Total Pressure Recovery"]

font = {'family': ['Times New Roman'],
        'color':  'black',
        'weight': 'bold',
        'size': 14,
        }
font_tick = {
    "family":"Times New Roman",
    "size":12,
    "weight":"heavy",
    "style":"normal"
}

plt.plot(x_data,y_data,"r")

plt.title("Total_pressure_recovery_along_streamwise_location",size=15,fontweight='bold',pad=30)
plt.xlabel('Streamwise_location(x_coordinate)',fontdict=font,labelpad=15)
plt.ylabel('Total Pressure Recovery',fontdict=font,labelpad=15)
plt.legend(["Pressure_ratio_12"],loc=0,shadow=True,edgecolor='black',borderpad=0.6,prop={'weight':"normal"})

plt.xticks(np.arange(0,0.200003,0.02),fontproperties=font_tick)
plt.yticks(np.arange(0,1.01,0.1),fontproperties=font_tick)

plt.xlim(0,0.2)
plt.ylim(0,1)
plt.grid(True)
plt.show()
